wiki.summary: Ranjithame is the first released single for the Tamil-Language movie "Varisu". It is the most popular song from the film and is sung by Thalapathy Vijay (who is also the lead actor in the movie) and M.M.Manasi. The music video and lyric video are both currently (12/02/2023) in the top 50 for trending songs on YouTube Read more on Last.fm.
